      "message": "It would just be a generic ZX_ERR_TIMED_OUT. So we could retry with backoff or something. I\u0027m not sure how to pick a useful time/strategy here for production code. In test code, I think it\u0027d be fine to wait indefinitely and document that, but I wouldn\u0027t want to use that in the general exception handler.",
